with param as (select to_date(?,'dd.mm.yyyy') d1, to_date(?,'dd.mm.yyyy') d2, ?::integer cln, ?::integer as dep), mon as (select '01' id,'января' m union all select '02','февраля' union all select '03','марта' union all select '04','апреля' union all select '05','мая' union all select '06','июня' union all select '07','июля' union all select '08','августа' union all select '09','сентября' union all select '10','октября' union all select '11','ноября' union all select '12','декабря'),
dep as (select dep.name from param join pim_department dep on dep.id = param.dep), q as ( select full_name||case when dep.name is not null then ', '||dep.name else '' end as cln_name, to_char(current_date,'dd') as c_dd, cm.m as c_mm, to_char(current_date,'yyyy') as c_yyyy, to_char(d1,'dd') as d1_dd, d1_m.m as d1_mm, to_char(d1,'yyyy') as d1_yyyy, to_char(d2,'dd') as d2_dd, d2_m.m as d2_mm, to_char(d2,'yyyy') as d2_yyyy from param left join pim_organization o on o.id=cln join mon cm on cm.id=to_char(current_date,'mm') join mon d1_m on d1_m.id=to_char(d1,'mm') join mon d2_m on d2_m.id=to_char(d2,'mm') left join dep on true)
select (select coalesce(v.value, s.default_value) from cmn_setting s join cmn_setting_value v on s.id = v.setting_id left join md_clinic cl on cl.scope_id = v.scope_id and cl.id = (select cln from param) where s.code = 'cz.atria.common.base.env.ContentStorageSettings.basexRestServiceUrl' and coalesce(cl.scope_id,1) = v.scope_id order by cl.scope_id -- чтобы NULL в последнюю очередь выбрался limit 1) as rest_path, '' a, (select adr__get_element_as_text(addr_id,'(2,s,0)(3,s,0)(4,s,0)(5,s,0)(6,s,0)(7,f,0)(8,s,0)(9,s,0)(10,s,0)') adr from pim_party_address ppa join param on cln=party_id join pim_party_addr_to_addr_type b on b.party_address_id=ppa.id and ppa.is_valid join pim_address_type t on t.id=b.address_type_id and t.code='POSTAL' limit 1) as adr,
(select cln_name from q) as cln_name,
(select concat(i.surname,' '||i.name,' '||i.patr_name) from param join pim_position pos on pos.organization_id=cln join pim_position_role r on r.id=pos.role_id and r.e_code='10002' join pim_employee_position ep on ep.position_id=pos.id join pim_employee e on e.id=ep.employee_id join pim_individual i on i.id=e.individual_id where ep.start_date <=param.d2 and (ep.end_date > param.d2 or ep.end_date is null) limit 1) as boss,
(select d1_dd || ' ' || d1_mm || ' ' || d1_yyyy || ' - ' || d2_dd || ' ' || d2_mm || ' ' || d2_yyyy from q left join mon on mon.id=d1_mm) as period, (select c_dd || ' ' || c_mm || ' ' || c_yyyy c from q left join mon on mon.id=d1_mm) as c, (select case when to_char(d1,'yyyy')=to_char(d2,'yyyy') and to_char(d1,'dd.mm')='01.01' and to_char(d2,'dd.mm')='31.12' then 'за '||to_char(d1,'yyyy')||' г.' else to_char(d1,'dd.mm.yyyy') || ' - ' || to_char(d2,'dd.mm.yyyy') end from param) as period1,
(select to_char(d2,'yy') from param) as f1, (select poc.code from param join pim_org_code poc on poc.org_id = cln join pim_code_type t on t.id = poc.type_id and t.code='OKPO' limit 1) as okpo, (select oc.value from pim_org_contact oc join pim_party_contact_type ct on oc.type_id=ct.id and lower(ct.name) like '%телефон%' join param on oc.org_id=cln limit 1) as phone
